    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Description\n\n`biome` uses a function for `cmd` that checks for a local binary at `{root_dir}/node_modules/.bin/biome` before falling back to the global executable. However, `oxlint` and `oxfmt` use static `cmd` arrays and won't pick up local binaries from `node_modules/.bin/`.",
